dct_description_sm: Map shows ethnic distribution by counties and municipalities under the P.R.C. occupation; international, provincial, prefectural and county boundaries; township and monasteries; provincial headquarters. Includes Index of Tibet counties with "autonomous" status, and counties traditionally or historically inhabited by Tibetans. "All regional boundaries ethnic distribution and names of counties and county headquarters are as designated by the P.R.C. as of July 1996, they may not conform to the actual situation and do not necessarily reflect the views of the Tibetan government in exile or any other concern authorities." Ancillary map: Population density.
